b'Ever wonder what "Broad Spectrum" actually means?\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3
There are two types of UV light: UVA and UVB. UVA rays account for 95% of the radiation that reaches the earth. They cause premature skin aging like wrinkles and dark spots. UVB rays are responsible for sunburns. Broad-spectrum sunscreens protect you from both UVA and UVB. Always lookout for a broad-spectrum SPF to protect your skin daily!\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3

b'#BeautyIsBoundless, with Huang Xuan.

Fifth film. The number of times Huang Xuan shot campaign films for us, with us. It all started back in 2016. In every campaign, Huang Xuan has showed us how to reinterpret what beauty means to men, time and again. He started his career as a dancer before getting into acting. Facing all kinds of doubts and frustrations, he remained persistent in the pursuit of his passion and dream career.

He continues to explore a variety of roles, portraying and breathing in different characters, enriching and touching the lives of everyone who watches his shows. Never giving up. Fearlessly committed. And now, he is one of the top actors in the industry and we are so proud of his success and achievement.

By inspiring others from his own experiences, Huang Xuan always encourages people around him to dare to step out of our own comfort zones and transcend any labels, every labels. Meet Lauren Wasser. At 24, Lauren had a full life: playing basketball, biking 30 miles or 48 kilometres a day, and pursuing a modeling career that started when she was 2 months old, appearing in Italian Vogue alongside her mother. But everything changed overnight in 2012 when Lauren developed Toxic Shock Syndrome, which ultimately took both of her legs. Yet Lauren chooses to wake up grateful for each day and excited to embrace her new legs, showing us what it means to be strong and be true to ourselves. Lauren is a true testament to beauty and resilience. With One Another. Without Limits. Our Future Is Beautiful. \xe2\x81\xa3

b'Ever wonder what "Broad Spectrum" actually means?
\xe2\x81\xa3
\xe2\x81\xa3There are two types of UV light: UVA and UVB. UVA rays account for 95% of the radiation that reaches the earth. They cause premature skin aging like wrinkles and dark spots. UVB rays are responsible for sunburns. Broad-spectrum sunscreens protect you from both UVA and UVB. Always lookout for a broad-spectrum SPF to protect your skin daily!

b'FOLDING OTAKU, since #1872.

In Japan, the careful wrapping of a gift is a way of expressing respect and appreciation toward the recipient, and that care can be perceived in each fold. The delicate art of folding a piece of wrapping paper dates back about 800 years to the Kamakura period of Japanese history.

Our folding specialists are artisans with exceptional skills in papercrafts and packaging. They study and examine all the different types of folds possible, and reflect a deep sense of respect to all products. Each package is beautifully completed with high speed, precision and care. By hand. With gratitude.

Inspired by Japanese tradition. Enriched with meaning and depth. A story wrapped in reverence. A story that indulges all senses. At @shiseido, we pride ourselves in creating the best performing product with the highest ever quality in the most beautiful form to all.

We are all about beauty. Your beauty.

b'Fermentation. An essential part of Japanese food culture. Fermented ingredients such as natto, amazake, soy sauce and miso are vital to Japanese cuisine and have been very well loved throughout history for their health and beauty benefits.

At the heart of the two new innovations, Beauty Smart Water and Giga-Hydrating Rich Cream, is the core fermentation philosophy- to harness nature\xe2\x80\x99s best in its most concentrated form, while respecting nature.

Beauty Smart Water is a 3-in-1 beauty water inspired by Japanese Amazake, a fermented rice drink. Helps to cleanse, hydrate and prime skin in one single step. With the help of fermented complexes, the smooth-textured water polishes skin gently, removing dirt, excess sebum, dead skin cells and light makeup while leaving moisturizing ingredients intact on your skin.

Giga-Hydrating Rich Cream is a deeply moisturizing cream that harnesses the power of fermented soybean extract and carrot cells to plump and hydrate skin, retaining moisture on skin for up to 48 hours. Fermented soybeans, or natto, is well known as Japan\xe2\x80\x99s classic superfood for its nutritional and beauty benefits.

b'Dawn breaks. A higher beauty evolved. A ritual to awaken skin, powered by the mythical Enmei herb.

Introducing the new #FutureSolutionLX Universal Defense and Total Protective Day Cream. Your ultimate rejuvenating daily skincare in the morning.

Treasured for its substantial healing properties since ancient times, the Enmei herb\xe2\x80\x99s roots run deep in Japanese folklore. The kanji character of en \xe2\x80\x9c\xe5\xbb\xb6\xe2\x80\x9d means extension and mei \xe2\x80\x9c\xe5\x91\xbd\xe2\x80\x9d means life. According to legend, the Enmei herb was used by Kobo Daishi, a monk of virtue, to save a sick traveler from death.

Inspired by this, our researchers travelled to the sacred Mount Koya in search of the plant. It was there that the master herb was handpicked and following careful cultivation under laboratory conditions, now exclusively formulated for Future Solution LX.
